sources.description:
Jungle Run: A search for their missing father turns deadly when sibling adventurers find themselves viciously attacked by jungle animals. But as they fight back against the relentless onslaught they start to realize something much more sinister may be behind the attacks.
2021. Stars: Richard Grieco, Alyson Gorske, Wade Hunt Williams

Megaboa: On a trip to Colombia, a group of college students heads into the rainforest to look for cave drawings. But a once thought to be extinct fifty-foot boa constrictor is out lurking in brush, hungry for blood.
2021. Stars: Eric Roberts, Michelle Elizabeth O'Shea, Emilia Torello
